<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Ludwig III. von Wittelsbach, Pfalzgraf bei Rhein</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Beilegung der Fehde zwischen Ludwigs Diener Heinrich von Hohenried und Wirich von Treuchtlingen, Reichsschultheiß zu Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_143" id="71r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_143_r3l4">Dem durchleuhtigen hochgepornen fürſten / vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> / <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ludvvigen / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r3l5"><expan>pfalcʒgrafe<ex>n</ex></expan> beÿ Rein / des heiligen Römiſchen Reichs Öberſter Truchſeſʒ / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r3l6">vnd fürſeher in den landen des Reins / cʒu <expan>Swab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd des frenckiſchen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r3l7">rechten / vnd hertʒog cʒu Beÿern  <note place="inline"><expan cert="low">d<ex>etur</ex></expan></note> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re<ex>n</ex></expan> / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_143_r3l8"><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / vns hat fürbracht her vvÿrich von <expan>Trewhtling<ex>en</ex></expan> Ritter / cʒu der cʒeit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r3l9">vnſer Schultheiſʒ / vvie etvvas vehe ſeÿ cʒwiſchen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> heinrichen von hehenriet / <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r3l10"><expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> / vnd Jm / Als das <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden der <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>e</ex></expan> her vvÿrich ſelber cʒu verſchreiben </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r3l11">maint / Nuͦ <expan>Roga<ex>mus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade darcʒu vvenden wöllet / daʒ die vehe abgetan / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r3l12">vnd die ſache cʒu gütlicheit kom / das wöllen etc <expan>antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / <expan>Sc<ex>ri</ex>pt<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>r</ex>ıa</expan> ıııj̃ <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> Margarethe / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_143" id="71r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Dem durchleuhtigen, hochgepornen fürsten und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Ludwigen, <expan>pfalczgrafe<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        bey Rein, des heiligen römischen reichs öberster truchsesz und fürseher in
                        den landen des Reins, czu <expan>Swab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und des
                        frenckischen rechten und herczog czu Beyern <app>
<note place="inline"><expan cert="low">d<ex>etur</ex></expan></note>
</app>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns hat fürbracht her Wyrich von
                                <expan>Trewhtling<ex>en</ex></expan>, ritter, czu der czeit unser
                        schultheisz, wie etwas vehe sey czwischen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        Heinrichen von Hehenriet, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, und im, als das <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
                        gnaden der <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>e</ex></expan> her Wyrich selber czu
                        verschreiben maint. Nuͦ <expan>roga<ex>mus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade darczu wenden wöllet, daz die vehe
                        abgetan und die sache czu gütlicheit kom. Das wöllen etc.
                                <expan>Antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>.
                            <expan>Sc<ex>ri</ex>pt<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>r</ex>ia</expan> iiii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
                        Margarethe.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
